On Wednesday, Russia's upper house of parliament unanimously approved the draft adoption ban, a retaliation against U.S. legislation enacted earlier this month that aims to punish alleged Russian human-rights violators. President Vladimir Putin could sign the draft into law as early as this week, a Kremlin spokesman...